Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:25.53,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}令人興奮難抑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:30.16,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}七色音符  永劫綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:31.41,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}心中忐忑不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:35.37,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}魔錘的烙印  現於暗礁之上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.45,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}玩夠了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:41.29,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}循於愛之真理  極光閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.33,0:22:42.92,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}差不多行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:48.59,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我們終將合二為一  翱翔於天際
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.72,0:22:54.26,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}浮華如焰火  喧囂過後終將凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:59.81,EDlrcCHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}刹那之間…迸發光芒萬丈！！
